JOHN WARREN, RESPONDENT, v. COUNTY OF HUDSON, APPELLANT. Submitted January 15, 1946 Decided April 30, 1946.

Before Case, Chibe Justice, and Justices Parker and Oliphant.

*92Eor the appellant, Thomas J. Armstrong (J. Emil Walscheid, on the brief). For the respondent, Eugene T. Sharkey. Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed, for the reasons stated in the full and careful opinion of Judge Roberson in the Common Pleas, and printed in 23 N. J. Mis. R. 252.
